org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Interaction

Interface SwMutualExclusionResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MutualExclusionResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SwInteractionResource, SwResource, SwSynchronizationResource, SynchronizationResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SwMutualExclusionResourceImpl

    public interface SwMutualExclusionResource
extends SwSynchronizationResource, MutualExclusionResource
    A representation of the model object 'Sw Mutual Exclusion Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Mechanism
    • Concurrent Access Protocol
    • Access Token Elements
    • Release Services
    • Acquire Services
    See Also:
    SW_InteractionPackage.getSwMutualExclusionResource()
